{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I'm going to make a order with a couple of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And then I'll go to-- I know where to go to hit Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I, I had a very good-- I-- they would take me because I have very good armaments.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I had two revolvers, an automatic, and about five grenades, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So they would take me this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mosty-- and there was a small [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] watering hole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I had to cross it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But what I saw is somebody threw in inside the pieces of implements.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I couldn't cross it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Everything was stuck, stuck out, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Well, I was caught in Mosty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I was brought to Volkovysk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I sat in Volkovysk until it was-- so all of '43, you know, '43, until approximately [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 24th, 24th of December.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I was-- I went through Gestapo in Volkovysk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I put the Gestapo, showed how stupid they are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And they decided, at the time, really the one who I'm telling that I-- my mother is from Georgia, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "It's a long story-- separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They send me to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "I had another interrogation with Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And they sent me to Stutthof, with 'SB,' [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Special treatment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POINTING] And on the third day, I was called out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, I found out that this was the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they put me the room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told me go to the next door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] On top was a, you know, a dangling electrical bulb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And right under the bulb, I look, you know, there is blood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a Hauptsturmfuhrer Meyer with a revolver.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went, turn around.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
